#: ../../source/concepts.md:64
msgid ""
"Positions are measured in metres, angles in radians, linear velocities in "
"metres per second, and angular velocities in radians per second. See {doc}"
"`Configure robots and obstacles <usage/configure_robots_obstacles>` for "
"configuration examples and velocity limits."
msgstr ""
"位置单位为米，角度单位为弧度，线速度单位为米每秒，角速度单位为弧度每秒。配置"
"示例和速度限制请参见 {doc}`配置机器人和障碍物 <usage/"
"configure_robots_obstacles>`。"

#: ../../source/concepts.md:69
msgid "Behaviors: deciding what to do"
msgstr "行为：决定要做什么"

#: ../../source/concepts.md:71
msgid ""
"A **behavior** maps an object's state (and, for reactive ones, its "
"neighbours) to a velocity command on every step. The built-ins are `dash` "
"(head straight to the goal), `rvo` (reciprocal velocity obstacles), and "
"`sfm` (social force model), plus the group behavior `orca` (optimal "
"reciprocal collision avoidance). You don't have to use a behavior at all; "
"instead, drive an object yourself by passing a command to "
"`env.step(action)`, or {doc}`register your own behavior <usage/"
"configure_behavior>`."
msgstr ""
"**行为**在每一步将对象的状态（对于反应式行为，还包括其邻居）映射为速度指令。"
"内置行为有 `dash`（直奔目标）、`rvo`（互惠速度障碍）和 `sfm`（社会力模型），"
"以及群体行为 `orca`（最优互惠避碰）。你也完全可以不使用行为——通过向 "
"`env.step(action)` 传入指令来自行驱动对象，或 {doc}`注册自定义行为 <usage/"
"configure_behavior>`。"

#: ../../source/concepts.md:73
msgid "Sensors: perceiving the world"
msgstr "传感器：感知世界"

#: ../../source/concepts.md:75
msgid ""
"**Sensors** are attached to objects and produce measurements from the world "
"each step: a 2D LiDAR, a 2D FMCW LiDAR (range *and* per-beam radial "
"velocity), and a field-of-view detector. Sensors are refreshed **after** "
"objects move, so a reading always reflects the latest world state."
msgstr ""
"**传感器**附着在对象上，每一步从世界产生测量：2D 激光雷达、2D FMCW 激光雷达"
"（距离*以及*每束的径向速度）和视场检测器。传感器在对象移动**之后**刷新，因此"
"读数始终反映最新的世界状态。"

#: ../../source/concepts.md:77
msgid "From YAML to a running scene"
msgstr "从 YAML 到运行的场景"

#: ../../source/concepts.md:79
msgid ""
"IR-SIM is **declarative**. The `world`, `robot`, and `obstacle` blocks in "
"your YAML are turned into `World` and object instances by an internal "
"factory, which is why you rarely write imperative setup code. You *describe* "
"the scene and IR-SIM builds it, so the same scenario file can be shared, "
"version-controlled, and reused across experiments. The {doc}`Configuration "
"<yaml_config/configuration>` reference documents every available key."
msgstr ""
"IR-SIM 是**声明式**的。YAML 中的 `world`、`robot` 与 `obstacle` 块由内部工厂"
"转化为 `World` 与对象实例——因此你很少需要编写命令式的初始化代码。你*描述*场"
"景，IR-SIM 负责构建，于是同一个场景文件可以被共享、纳入版本控制，并在不同实验"
"间复用。{doc}`配置 <yaml_config/configuration>` 参考记录了每一个可用的配置"
"键。"

